<paragraph blockId="23.[313,1269,1453,1733]" pageId="23" pageNumber="359">
<emphasis box="[353,461,1455,1478]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="359">Diagnosis</emphasis>
. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hansen" authorityYear="1916" box="[480,642,1454,1478]" class="Malacostraca" family="Haploniscidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Isopoda" pageId="23" pageNumber="359" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Haploniscidae</taxonomicName>
with pereonites 5â€“7 fused with pleotelson to form a consolidated robust segment. Cephalon produced into rostral lobe or small conical process. Antenna 2 with article 3 lacking spinous process. Uropods either reduced or absent. Pleotelson either truncated or rounded posteriorly with posterolateral projection small. Body capable of rolling as a round ball.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="23.[313,1269,1453,1733]" pageId="23" pageNumber="359">
<emphasis box="[353,460,1613,1637]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="359">Remarks.</emphasis>
This genus presently includes 10 species, including three new species discovered in this study. Two species are known from the Pacific: 
<taxonomicName authority="Birstein, 1971" authorityName="Birstein" authorityYear="1971" class="Malacostraca" family="Haploniscidae" genus="Hydroniscus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Isopoda" pageId="23" pageNumber="359" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="minutus">
<emphasis box="[1045,1167,1646,1669]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="359">H. minutus</emphasis>
Birstein, 1971
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Birstein, 1963" authorityName="Birstein" authorityYear="1963" box="[436,724,1677,1701]" class="Malacostraca" family="Haploniscidae" genus="Hydroniscus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Isopoda" pageId="23" pageNumber="359" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vitjazi">
<emphasis box="[436,545,1678,1701]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="359">H. vitjazi</emphasis>
Birstein, 1963
</taxonomicName>
. Seven species are known from the Atlantic: 
<taxonomicName authority="Hansen, 1916" authorityName="Hansen" authorityYear="1916" box="[313,591,1709,1733]" class="Malacostraca" family="Haploniscidae" genus="Hydroniscus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Isopoda" pageId="23" pageNumber="359" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="abyssi">
<emphasis box="[313,420,1709,1733]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="359">H. abyssi</emphasis>
Hansen, 1916
</taxonomicName>
